Text: Weekly Portfolio Summary My Ameritrade PortfolioHere is the Weekly Analysis Summary you have subscribed to as part of Ameritrades Report Alert Service This service provides an Excel workbook containing separate areas of analysis on two different worksheets After opening the attached file use the tabs at the bottom of the spreadsheet to move between worksheets Weekly Summary Worksheet Includes personalized market and portfolio summary charts showing your portfolios performance over a week month month or month period of time in relation to one of popular indices This worksheet also graphically represents the individual positions within your portfolio through a performance by position bar chart a value and sector distribution pie chart and a portfolio table grid Stock Charts Worksheet Includes price and volume performance graphs for every stock in your portfolio along with stock trading fundamentals over a one week or one month period If prompted please be sure to choose Enable Macros when you open the workbook Thank you for using Ameritrades Report Alert Service Powered by Strategycom Email us at mailto meritradecom if you have questions regarding this alert Change your font to a fixedwidth ie Courier if the columns are not aligned Return to Ameritrade to place an order or change your settings Quotes supplied by Thomson Financial Quotes delayed at least minutes for NYSE and AMEX minutes for NASDAQ and minutes for CBOT and CME WklySummaryxls
